{
  "levelId": "sf-01",
  "chapterId": "sf-01",
  "worldId": "sci-fi",
  "title": "星港登船舱：看见信号",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "arrival",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/sci-fi/sf-01.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "星港的玻璃穹顶亮起一颗蓝色光点。小小探险家和星尘伙伴准备出发，去寻找回家的星图。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是星港登船舱。我们先把“看见信号”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到光核在轻轻嗡鸣，信号就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先看清蓝色航线，再做一个安全的小动作。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "scan",
          "prompt": "启动扫描器，找出会闪烁的蓝色信号。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "扫描蓝色光点",
              "feedback": "扫描成功！信号记下来了。"
            },
            {
              "label": "打开舱门灯",
              "feedback": "灯亮了，蓝色光点也跟着眨了眨。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，扫描蓝色光点让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "扫描光点后，隐藏的星尘轨迹露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条轨迹和星图接起来，下一站就会亮起。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这束光，它会带我们穿过下一段星际航线。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "信号说：去月环补给站。我们出发！",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
        "characters": [
          "narrator",
